CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 12, 1955, pg. B14 reads: " 'New Faces' - That's the theme of the Young People's Group of Wesley Center AME Zion Church as it prepares for the year's program. Sunday, the group held one of its social events at the church.  Left to right, front row: Patricia Prattis and "Danny" McClelland.  Second row: Elder Gant, Samuel Wilkins, Mrs. Mamie Wadkins, sponsor, and Herschelle Sullivan. - Harris Photo.
TitMainTitle: Patricia Prattis and "Danny" McClelland holding document, standing in front of left to right: Elder Gant, Samuel Wilkins, Mamie Wadkins, and Herschelle Sullivan, for Young People's Group of Wesley Center AME Zion Church
